{
  "name": "Automate NDA Signing with Form Input and AllSign",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📋 NDA Automation with AllSign\n\nThis workflow automates the entire NDA signing process:\n\n1. **A form** collects signer details and contract terms\n2. **Variables are mapped** to fill the DOCX template\n3. **The template is downloaded** from a public URL\n4. **AllSign creates the document** and sends signing invitations automatically\n\n> **Time saved:** What used to take 15+ minutes of manual work now runs in seconds.",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "sticky-overview",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [180, -60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔗 Template URL Setup\n\n**⚠️ Replace the URL** in the HTTP Request node with your hosted DOCX template.\n\nOptions to host:\n- GitHub Release asset\n- S3 / CloudFront bucket\n- Any public file server\n\nYou can also use an **n8n variable** (`$vars.nda_template_url`) to keep the URL configurable.",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 300,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "sticky-template-url",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [640, -60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔑 Credentials\n\n1. Go to **Credentials → Add → AllSign API**\n2. Paste your API Key from [dashboard.allsign.io/developers/api-keys](https://dashboard.allsign.io/developers/api-keys)\n3. Click **Save** — the connection test runs automatically\n\n> Free trial keys start with `allsign_test_sk_...`",
        "height": 230,
        "width": 300,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "sticky-credentials",
      "name": "Sticky Note2",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [960, -60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 💡 Tips\n\n- **Template variables** like `{{ client_name }}` in the DOCX are auto-replaced with form values\n- **WhatsApp** is optional — leave blank to send by email only\n- **Signature validations** can be customized in the AllSign node (FEA, NOM-151, eIDAS, biometric, etc.)",
        "height": 220,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "sticky-tips",
      "name": "Sticky Note3",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [180, 520]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "formTitle": "NDA Request Form",
        "formDescription": "Fill out this form to generate and send a Non-Disclosure Agreement for electronic signature via AllSign.",
        "formFields": {
          "values": [
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Client Full Name",
              "fieldType": "text",
              "requiredField": true,
              "placeholder": "e.g. Jane Smith"
            },
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Client Email",
              "fieldType": "email",
              "requiredField": true,
              "placeholder": "e.g. jane@company.com"
            },
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Client WhatsApp (Optional)",
              "fieldType": "text",
              "requiredField": false,
              "placeholder": "e.g. +525512345678"
            },
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Company Name (Disclosing Party)",
              "fieldType": "text",
              "requiredField": true,
              "placeholder": "e.g. Acme Corp"
            },
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Project Description",
              "fieldType": "text",
              "requiredField": true,
              "placeholder": "e.g. Software development collaboration for Project X"
            },
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Effective Date",
              "fieldType": "date",
              "requiredField": true
            },
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Confidentiality Period",
              "fieldType": "dropdown",
              "requiredField": true,
              "fieldOptions": {
                "values": [
                  { "option": "1 year" },
                  { "option": "2 years" },
                  { "option": "3 years" },
                  { "option": "5 years" },
                  { "option": "Indefinite" }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "fieldLabel": "Governing Law / Jurisdiction",
              "fieldType": "dropdown",
              "requiredField": true,
              "fieldOptions": {
                "values": [
                  { "option": "Mexico City, Mexico" },
                  { "option": "State of California, USA" },
                  { "option": "Madrid, Spain" },
                  { "option": "Bogotá, Colombia" },
                  { "option": "Buenos Aires, Argentina" },
                  { "option": "London, United Kingdom" }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "respondToWebhook": true,
          "formSubmittedText": "✅ Your NDA has been created and sent for signature!\n\nThe signer will receive an invitation via email (and WhatsApp if provided) to review and sign the NDA electronically."
        }
      },
      "id": "form-trigger",
      "name": "NDA Request Form",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [220, 300],
      "webhookId": "nda-form-allsign"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "manual",
        "duplicateItem": false,
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "set-doc-name",
              "name": "documentName",
              "value": "=NDA - {{ $json['Client Full Name'] }} - {{ $json['Company Name (Disclosing Party)'] }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "set-client-name",
              "name": "clientName",
              "value": "={{ $json['Client Full Name'] }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "set-client-email",
              "name": "clientEmail",
              "value": "={{ $json['Client Email'] }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "set-client-whatsapp",
              "name": "clientWhatsapp",
              "value": "={{ $json['Client WhatsApp (Optional)'] || '' }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "set-company-name",
              "name": "companyName",
              "value": "={{ $json['Company Name (Disclosing Party)'] }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "set-project-desc",
              "name": "projectDescription",
              "value": "={{ $json['Project Description'] }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "set-eff-date",
              "name": "effectiveDate",
              "value": "={{ $json['Effective Date'] }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "set-conf-period",
              "name": "confidentialityPeriod",
              "value": "={{ $json['Confidentiality Period'] }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "set-gov-law",
              "name": "governingLaw",
              "value": "={{ $json['Governing Law / Jurisdiction'] }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "set-template-vars",
              "name": "templateVariablesJson",
              "value": "={{ JSON.stringify({ client_name: $json['Client Full Name'], company_name: $json['Company Name (Disclosing Party)'], effective_date: $json['Effective Date'], project_description: $json['Project Description'], confidentiality_period: $json['Confidentiality Period'], governing_law: $json['Governing Law / Jurisdiction'] }) }}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "set-variables",
      "name": "Map Form to Template Variables",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [480, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $vars.nda_template_url || 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AllSign-io/n8n-nodes-allsign/main/examples/NDA_Template_AllSign.docx' }}",
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "responseFormat": "file"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "download-template",
      "name": "Download NDA Template (DOCX)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [740, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "documentName": "={{ $('Map Form to Template Variables').item.json.documentName }}",
        "fileSource": "binary",
        "binaryProperty": "data",
        "signers": {
          "signerValues": [
            {
              "name": "={{ $('Map Form to Template Variables').item.json.clientName }}",
              "email": "={{ $('Map Form to Template Variables').item.json.clientEmail }}",
              "whatsapp": "={{ $('Map Form to Template Variables').item.json.clientWhatsapp }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "signatureValidations": {
          "verifyAutografa": true
        },
        "configuration": {
          "sendInvitations": true,
          "templateVariables": "={{ $('Map Form to Template Variables').item.json.templateVariablesJson }}"
        }
      },
      "id": "allsign-create",
      "name": "AllSign: Create & Send NDA",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-allsign.allsign",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1000, 300],
      "credentials": {
        "allSignApi": {
          "id": "",
          "name": "AllSign API"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "NDA Request Form": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Map Form to Template Variables",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Map Form to Template Variables": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Download NDA Template (DOCX)",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Download NDA Template (DOCX)": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "AllSign: Create & Send NDA",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  },
  "pinData": {},
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "staticData": null,
  "tags": [
    { "name": "NDA" },
    { "name": "E-Signature" },
    { "name": "AllSign" },
    { "name": "Document Automation" },
    { "name": "Form" }
  ],
  "triggerCount": 1,
  "meta": {
    "templateId": "allsign-nda-form-automation",
    "templateCredsSetupCompleted": false,
    "instanceId": ""
  }
}
